E4Plus1.uk.description: SuperShowerBabyBowl: Jay is hosting a Super Bowl party, while Claire hosts a baby shower for Haley - and they're both at Jay's house. What could possibly go wrong? (S10 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Art of Negotiation: When Dave is up for promotion, Calvin tries to help him negotiate a raise from his penny-pinching new boss. (S5 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Hot Prospect: When Calvin stumbles upon a big business opportunity, he must convince Malcolm to help him to seal the deal. (S5 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Mercedes and Ste spiral as loved ones step in to help. Donny's concerns over Dodger continue to grow. And there's turmoil for one family.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Ste tries to do the right thing, but a text leads Lucas to jump to conclusions. Elsewhere, a resident fights to keep the past hidden and Liberty tries to pull her family back together.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs

E4Plus1.uk.description: I'm Dancing as Fat as I Can: Homer's broken promise infuriates Marge, so he studies ballroom dancing to try to win her back. (S30 Ep13/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Geology Elevation: Sheldon can't contain his jealousy when he hears that his university colleague, Bert the geologist, has won a prestigious fellowship. (S10 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Property Division Collision: Sheldon, Amy, Leonard and Penny attempt to divide up all their possessions. It doesn't go well. (S10 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family

E4Plus1.uk.description: The Plimpton Stimulation: When Sheldon meets a famous physicist online, he invites her over to the apartment, where she spends her time flirting with Leonard. (S3 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Staircase Implementation: Leonard tells Penny about how he and Sheldon became friends, and the origins of the roommate agreement. (S3 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Lunar Excitation: Raj registers Sheldon for online dating and finds the perfect match: the female version of Sheldon. Penny seduces Leonard while she's drunk. (S3 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Robotic Manipulation: Penny tags along to Sheldon's first date with a woman he's been texting for months. Howard finds a new use for a robotic arm. (S4 Ep1)

Film4.uk.title: Free Guy
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Comedy action starring Ryan Reynolds. Guy lives in Free City. Free City isn't real. Nor is Guy. It's all a big online game. Can he take down the corrupt game publisher?

Film4.uk.title: Werewolves Within
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Comedy horror with Milana Vayntrub. A park ranger is sent to a town where everyone is at each other's throats, figuratively at first, but then literally. Is a werewolf to blame?

Film4.uk.title: Carrington, VC
Film4.uk.description: (1954) Anthony Asquith's vivid and subtle courtroom drama casts David Niven as the eponymous officer accused of stealing army money and going absent without leave.

Film4.uk.title: Pool of London
Film4.uk.description: (1951) Classic Ealing thriller filmed in a documentary style, starring Bonar Colleano as a sailor whose smuggling activities lead to him being suspected of murder and going on the run.

Film4.uk.title: The Fallen Idol
Film4.uk.description: (1948) Adaptation of Graham Greene's story with Ralph Richardson and Bobby Henrey. A butler who is accused of murdering his wife, has only a schoolboy to fight his corner.

Film4.uk.title: Fatherhood
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Heartfelt fact-based comedy-drama. Kevin Hart stars as a widower who is suddenly sprung into single fatherhood after his wife dies a day after giving birth.

Film4.uk.title: Central Intelligence
Film4.uk.description: (2016) Action-comedy with Dwayne Johnson and Kevin Hart. Two former school buddies team up to thwart a terrorist plot. But things may not be as they seem. With Amy Ryan and Jason Bateman.

Film4.uk.title: Violent Night
Film4.uk.description: (2022) A gang of violent home-invaders find out the hard way that you REALLY don't want to be on Santa's naughty list, in Tommy Wirkola's dark, violent Christmas comedy. With David Harbour.

Film4.uk.title: S.W.A.T.
Film4.uk.description: (2003) Action with Colin Farrell and Samuel L Jackson. A loose canon joins an elite force to escort a fugitive to chokey. But the baddie's put a reward out for help with his escape.

Film4.uk.title: Mothering Sunday
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Romantic drama with Odessa Young and Olivia Colman. In 20s England, a writer working as a maid has a passionate affair with the rich boy next door. It's not considered a good match.

Film4.uk.title: Cover Girl
Film4.uk.description: (1944) Rita Hayworth and Gene Kelly star in Charles Vidor's Technicolor comedy musical about a chorus girl's rise to fame. Featuring songs and a score from Jerome Kern and Ira Gershwin.

Film4.uk.title: Gift Horse
Film4.uk.description: (1952) War drama. Trevor Howard plays the captain of an ageing US warship, gifted to the British navy, which is chosen to lead the raid on Saint-Nazaire in 1942. With Richard Attenborough.

Film4.uk.title: The Moonraker
Film4.uk.description: (1958) Romantic thriller. George Baker stars as a heroic Cavalier horseman, beating off the Roundhead foe as he single-handedly smuggles the country's aristocracy to safety in France.

Film4.uk.title: Instant Family
Film4.uk.description: (2018) Comedy. Mark Wahlberg and Rose Byrne star as a couple whose orderly lives are disrupted when they foster three kids. Based on director Sean Anders' own experience.

Film4.uk.title: Transporter 2

Film4.uk.title: Inglourious Basterds
Film4.uk.description: (2009) Quentin Tarantino's World War II action-adventure. Jewish American soldiers go Nazi-hunting in occupied France. With Brad Pitt, Diane Kruger, Christoph Waltz and Michael Fassbender.

Film4.uk.title: A Private Function
Film4.uk.description: (1984) Michael Palin and Maggie Smith star in Alan Bennett's comedy set in food-rationed post-war Britain. In 1947, an illegally owned pig is secretly being fattened for a royal feast.

Film4Plus1.uk.title: Central Intelligence

Film4Plus1.uk.title: Violent Night
Film4Plus1.uk.description: (2022) A gang of violent home-invaders find out the hard way that you REALLY don't want to be on Santa's naughty list, in Tommy Wirkola's dark, violent Christmas comedy. With David Harbour.

Film4Plus1.uk.title: S.W.A.T.
Film4Plus1.uk.description: (2003) Action with Colin Farrell and Samuel L Jackson. A loose canon joins an elite force to escort a fugitive to chokey. But the baddie's put a reward out for help with his escape.

Film4Plus1.uk.title: Mothering Sunday
Film4Plus1.uk.description: (2021) Romantic drama with Odessa Young and Olivia Colman. In 20s England, a writer working as a maid has a passionate affair with the rich boy next door. It's not considered a good match.

Film4Plus1.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4Plus1.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4Plus1.uk.title: Arizona Raiders
Film4Plus1.uk.description: (1965) William Whitney's brutal western. Two former Confederate rebels are offered their freedom if they can track, catch or even kill their former gang mates. Starring Audie Murphy.

Film4Plus1.uk.title: Cover Girl
Film4Plus1.uk.description: (1944) Rita Hayworth and Gene Kelly star in Charles Vidor's Technicolor comedy musical about a chorus girl's rise to fame. Featuring songs and a score from Jerome Kern and Ira Gershwin.

Film4Plus1.uk.title: Gift Horse
Film4Plus1.uk.description: (1952) War drama. Trevor Howard plays the captain of an ageing US warship, gifted to the British navy, which is chosen to lead the raid on Saint-Nazaire in 1942. With Richard Attenborough.

Film4Plus1.uk.title: The Moonraker
Film4Plus1.uk.description: (1958) Romantic thriller. George Baker stars as a heroic Cavalier horseman, beating off the Roundhead foe as he single-handedly smuggles the country's aristocracy to safety in France.

Film4Plus1.uk.title: Instant Family
Film4Plus1.uk.description: (2018) Comedy. Mark Wahlberg and Rose Byrne star as a couple whose orderly lives are disrupted when they foster three kids. Based on director Sean Anders' own experience.

Film4Plus1.uk.title: Transporter 2

Film4Plus1.uk.title: Inglourious Basterds
Film4Plus1.uk.description: (2009) Quentin Tarantino's World War II action-adventure. Jewish American soldiers go Nazi-hunting in occupied France. With Brad Pitt, Diane Kruger, Christoph Waltz and Michael Fassbender.

Film4Plus1.uk.title: A Private Function
Film4Plus1.uk.description: (1984) Michael Palin and Maggie Smith star in Alan Bennett's comedy set in food-rationed post-war Britain. In 1947, an illegally owned pig is secretly being fattened for a royal feast.

Film4Plus1.uk.title: The Winslow Boy

Film4Plus1.uk.title: Hell Is a City
